#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
redis-tool — Redis Cluster Lifecycle CLI
=========================================
Provisions, operates, and performs zero-downtime rolling upgrades
on a 6-node Redis Cluster (3M + 3R) with Ansible automation.

Usage:
    ./redis-tool provision --version 7.0.15 --masters 3 --replicas-per-master 1
    ./redis-tool data seed --keys 1000
    ./redis-tool data verify
    ./redis-tool status
    ./redis-tool upgrade --target-version 7.2.6 --strategy rolling
    ./redis-tool verify --full
    ./redis-tool infra up|down
"""

